snippet.title: Xenoverse: Per Aspera Ad Astra - Global Release
snippet.description:
A lot of new Creatures to catch, 50 hours of gameplay, new Trainers, new game features and a completely new exciting story await you in "Xenoverse: Per Aspera Ad Astra", coming out 02/10/2021. Only ITA and ENG!
Download here:  https://mega.nz/file/pCBWBaxK#5LZjsYXaMu3CQhX9zz0EkSeTqIeqmyVD39ME8TYZj6U
